Content: Hi my name is max. I just recently left my clan rize and I’m going to start up a new one called ShaTTered. It’s going to be based off of players who r insane at sniping and can do it naturally. If you believe you possess this skill or “power” join our discord server and contact a admin or member through that. To get a invite to our discord server dm ME rn on discord. These r the servers youre aloud to be on to join — NA east or west and EU - any platform is welcome. We’re also looking for GFX designers_ thumbnail designers and editors. If you have any other ideas for non-player roles_ we are always interested in any ideas you may have. Any questions feel free to dm me. Be patient for a response. Thank you for u time and have a amazing day/night
